          "text": "1. Overview"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The stored procedure "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "aspnet_Membership_GetPasswordWithFormat",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " is designed to retrieve a user's password and related information from the membership database in a specific format. It also has the capability to update the user's last login and activity dates if specified. This procedure is part of the ASP.NET Membership Provider model, which manages user authentication and authorization."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
