      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The procedure involves multiple database operations, including SELECT and UPDATE statements, and conditional logic to handle different scenarios such as user lockout and approval status. The complexity arises from the need to manage multiple user states and update operations based on input parameters."
        }
